item.title: Prayer bpn13455 in Chichewa
item.description: O Inu Wamphamvu zonse! Ine ndine wochimwa, koma Inu Ndinu Wokhululukira! Ine ndiri wosakwanira, koma Inu muli wachisoni! Inde ndiri mumdima wa uchimo koma Inu Ndinu nyali ya Chikhululukiro! O Inu Mulungu Wachifundo! Khululukirani machimo anga, ndipatseni mphatso Zanu, iwalani mphulupulu zanga, ndichinjirizeni ndi kundimiza mâ€™kasupe wa chipiliro Chanu ndipo ndichizeni ine kudwala konse ndi matenda. Ndiyeretseni ndi kundidalitsa ndipo ndipatseni gawo kuchokera ku mbvumbi wakuyera, mwakuti chisoni ndi kusakondwa zichoke ndipo chisangalalo ndi chimwemwe zitsike.
